---
name: update-spec
description: Update spec.md — criteria, status, scope, or dependencies.
---

Configuration:
- SPEC_NAME: 001-initial-setup

Path resolution:
- SPEC_FILE = .specify/specs/{SPEC_NAME}/spec.md
- PLAN_FILE = .specify/specs/{SPEC_NAME}/plan.md
- TASKS_FILE = .specify/specs/{SPEC_NAME}/tasks.md

Mandatory reading order:

1. .github/copilot-instructions.md
2. .specify/memory/constitution.md
3. {SPEC_FILE}
4. {PLAN_FILE}
5. {TASKS_FILE}

Change request: <!-- describe what to add, remove, or modify in spec.md -->

Execution rules:

1. Read {SPEC_FILE} in full before changing anything.
2. Apply the requested change precisely — do not rewrite unrelated sections.
3. Preserve existing structure, formatting, and section order.
4. Adding criteria: append to Acceptance Criteria. Do not renumber existing ones.
5. Removing criteria: mark as strikethrough with reason — never hard-delete unless asked.
6. Updating status: only valid transitions are draft → in-progress → complete.
7. If the change contradicts the constitution, flag it and stop.
8. After updating, check if tasks.md needs new tasks to cover added criteria.

Required output:
1. What changed in spec.md (before/after summary per section).
2. Whether plan.md or tasks.md need follow-up updates.
3. Whether the change is consistent with the constitution.
